        For their part, <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">Coyne</ENAMEX> and <ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">Orr</ENAMEX> feel that the prevalence of sympatric speciation is an
        <ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">empirical issue</ENAMEX> (but a very difficult one), and undertake a broad, detailed review. They
