        <ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">Orr</ENAMEX> note weaknesses in <NUMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">all three</NUMEX> cases, as well as in examples of <ENAMEX TYPE="DISEASE">‚Äúhost races‚Äù</ENAMEX> that have
        been advanced as species 
        in statu nascendi . <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">Coyne</ENAMEX> and <ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">Orr</ENAMEX>'s conclusion echoes <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">Gavrilets's</ENAMEX>: <NUMEX TYPE="MONEY">‚</NUMEX>ÄúIt is
